desc: At Funky Cellar we supply a large range of cheeses, charcuterie, wines (nature or conventional), beers and delicatessen product from around Europe, mainly french though. You can also discover more about our Bar à fromage (cheese bar) and our tastings events, online or with us at the Old Spitafield Market.

layout.text: Delicatessen, Fromagerie, Wine Shop and Bar, selling quality vintage goods. Funky Cellar is a concept store, bathed in 70s décor.
